entries.s_11: Can you help me recover some supplies we lost in the lower levels?
entries.s_15: Oh good. You'll have to be fast though. Security droids will notice all the noise and investigate. You'll only have about ten minutes once you're down there.
entries.s_19: Could find all of the supplies before having to clear out? Well, thanks for trying. Let me know if you want to try again.
entries.s_20: Ah, okay. I think I get it. I'll find someone else.
entries.s_4: These supplies will really help! Thank you!!
entries.s_9: We're looking good at the moment, but ya never know when we might need more help. Check back later.
